5	Lembaga Keuangan Mikro Syariah 	Divisi Lembaga Keuangan Mikro Syariah mempunyai tugas melakukan peny1apan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang lembaga keuangan mikro syariah.	3	Keuangan Sosial Syariah	Islamic Microfinance Institution	The Sharia Microfinance Institutions Division is responsible for preparing materials for recommendation formulation, coordinating the drafting and implementation, as well as preparing materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia microfinance institutions.
7	Kemitraan dan Akselerasi Usaha Syariah 	Divisi Kemitraan dan Akselerasi Usaha Syariah mempunyai tugas melakukan penyiapan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang kemitraan dan akselerasi usaha syariah.                                        	4	Bisnis dan Kewirausahaan Syariah	Partnership and Acceleration of Sharia Business	The Division of Sharia Business Partnerships and Acceleration is responsible for preparing materials for formulating recommendations, coordinating the formulation and implementation, as well as preparing materials for monitoring and evaluating the policy direction and strategic programs in the field of sharia business partnerships and enterprise acceleration.        
14	Pengembangan Halal Assurance System	Divisi Pengembangan Halal Assurance System mempunyai tugas melakukan penyiapan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang pengembangan halal assurance system.	1	Industri Produk Halal	Halal Assurance System Development	The Halal Assurance System Development Division is responsible for preparing materials for recommendation formulation, coordinating the drafting and implementation, as well as monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of halal assurance system development.
