11	Promosi dan Kerja Sama Strategis	Divisi Promosi dan Kerja Sama Strategis mempunyai tugas melakukan peny1apan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang promosi dan kerja sama strategis ekonomi dan keuangan syariah.	5	Infrastruktur Ekosistem Syariah	Promotion and Strategic Cooperation	The Division of Promotion and Strategic Cooperation is responsible for preparing materials for formulating recommendations, coordinating the formulation and implementation, as well as monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of promotion and strategic cooperation in Islamic economics and finance.
3	Pasar Modal Syariah	Divisi Pasar Modal Syariah mempunyai tugas melakukan penyiapan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang pasar modal syariah.	2	Jasa Keuangan Syariah	Sharia Capital Market	The Sharia Capital Market Division is responsible for preparing materials for recommendation formulation, coordinating the drafting and implementation, as well as preparing materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia capital markets.
4	Dana Sosial Syariah 	Divisi Dana Sosial Syariah mempunyai tugas melakukan penyiapan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang dana sosial syariah.	3	Keuangan Sosial Syariah	Sharia Social Fund	The Sharia Social Fund Division is responsible for preparing materials for recommendation formulation, coordinating the drafting and implementation, as well as preparing materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia social funds.
9	Bisnis Digital dan Pusat Data Ekonomi Syariah	Divisi Bisnis Digital dan Pusat Data Ekonomi Syariah mempunyai tugas:\r\n1. koordinasi, pengembangan, sinkronisasi, integrasi kebijakan, program dan ekosistem bisnis digital syariah di bidang Infrastruktur, SDM, Iklim Bisnis, Keamanan Siber, Riset, Inovasi, Pengembangan Usaha, Pendanaan, Investasi, Kebijakan dan Regulasi, serta mendorong inovasi digital, dan mengakselerasi transformasi digital bisnis syariah di Indonesia\r\n2. Koordinasi, menyusun dan melaksanakan kebijakan layanan serta tata kelola data Ekonomi Syariah, manajemen data,  infrastruktur dan fasilitas pusat data, jaringan komunikasi data, aplikasi, basis data dan keamanan informasi data. 	4	Bisnis dan Kewirausahaan Syariah	Digital Business and Islamic Economic Data Center	The Digital Business and Sharia Economic Data Center Division has the following duties:\r\n1. Coordinating, developing, synchronizing, and integrating policies, programs, and the digital Sharia business ecosystem in the areas of Infrastructure, Human Resources, Business Climate, Cybersecurity, Research, Innovation, Business Development, Funding, Investment, Policy and Regulation, as well as encouraging digital innovation and accelerating the digital transformation of Sharia businesses in Indonesia.\r\n2. Coordinating, formulating, and implementing policies for Sharia Economic data services and governance, data management, data center infrastructure and facilities, data communication networks, applications, databases, and data information security.
6	Inklusi Keuangan Syariah	Divisi Inklusi Keuangan Syariah mempunyai tugas melakukan penyiapan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang inklusi keuangan syariah.                        	3	Keuangan Sosial Syariah	Islamic Financial Inclusion	The Sharia Financial Inclusion Division is responsible for preparing materials for recommendation formulation, coordinating the drafting and implementation, as well as preparing materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia financial inclusion.                                      
13	Riset Ekonomi Syariah	Divisi Riset Ekonomi Syariah mempunyai tugas melakukan penyiapan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang riset ekonomi dan keuangan syariah.	5	Infrastruktur Ekosistem Syariah	Islamic Economic Research	The Sharia Economic Research Division is responsible for preparing materials for recommendation formulation, coordinating the drafting and implementation, as well as preparing materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia economic and financial research.
12	Pengembagan SDM Ekonomi Syariah	Divisi Pengembangan SDM mempunyai tugas melakukan Ekonomi Syariah penyiapan bahan rumusan rekomendasi, bahan koordinasi perumusan dan pelaksanaan, serta bahan pemantauan dan evaluasi arah kebijakan dan program strategis di bidang pengembangan sumber daya manusia ekonomi                                  	5	Infrastruktur Ekosistem Syariah	Development of Sharia Economic Human Resources	The Human Resource Development Division is responsible for preparing materials for recommendation formulation, coordinating the drafting and implementation, as well as preparing materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of human resource development for sharia economy.                 
