nd finance.</p><p>In carrying out its duties, the Directorate of Sharia Business and Entrepreneurship performs the following functions:</p><ol start="1"><li><p>Preparation of materials for formulating recommendations, coordination of formulation and implementation, as well as monitoring and evaluation materials for policy directions and strategic programs in the field of sharia business partnerships and enterprise acceleration;</p></li><li><p>Preparation of materials for formulating recommendations, coordination of formulation and implementation, as well as monitoring and evaluation materials for policy directions and strategic programs in the field of sharia business incubation;</p></li><li><p>Preparation of materials for formulating recommendations, coordination of formulation and implementation, as well as monitoring and evaluation materials for policy directions and strategic programs in the field of sharia digital business; and</p></li><li><p>Management of national data on the sharia economy and finance</p></li></ol>	kneks	https://cms.kneks.go.id/uploads/directorat/images/sme.svg	https://cms.kneks.go.id/uploads/directorat/images/banners-1763010940157.jpeg	10	Banten
