 of drafting and implementation, and materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of non-bank sharia financial services; and</li><li>Preparation of materials for recommendation formulation, coordination of drafting and implementation, and materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia capital markets.</li></ol><p></p><div></div>	kneks	https://cms.kneks.go.id/uploads/directorat/images/jasa.svg	https://cms.kneks.go.id/uploads/directorat/images/banners-1763787996930.jpeg	15	Jawa Timur
