on, coordination of drafting and implementation, and materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia microfinance institutions; and</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 0.84rem;">Preparation of materials for recommendation formulation, coordination of drafting and implementation, and materials for monitoring and evaluating the direction of policies and strategic programs in the field of sharia financial inclusion.</span></li></ol>	kneks	https://cms.kneks.go.id/uploads/directorat/images/sosial.svg	https://webdev.rifhandi.com/uploads/directorat/images/1.png	19	Kalimantan Barat
